---
title: Chicken and Bulgur Salad  with bell peppers and Greek style cheese
description: This chicken and bulgur is lightly spiced with flavours from the Middle East. It's also adorned with a delicious paprika aioli dressing and a generous helping of salty crumbled Greek style cheese.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/HF_Y24_R18_W01_IE_IEQCC18419-2_Main_1high-c2c88334.jpg
pdf: https://www.hellofresh.ie/recipecards/card/6526ab5cbe675f371f8b639d.pdf
